*hpricot-0.8 (08 May 2009)

  08 May 2009; Diego E. Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org> +hpricot-0.8.ebuild:
  Version bump and use a fake spec instead of a gem.

  29 Dec 2008; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> -hpricot-0.6.164.ebuild:
  Remove known to be broken version since we can't fix the gem easily.

